"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756902","Home Office","false","2017-09-07","<p>On 16 July 2017, the Home Secretary announced that there will be a review of the Poisons Act 1972 to help combat the horrendous crimes that are being committed on our streets. This work, done in conjunction with the Ministry of Justice and the Police Service is ongoing; details of which will be released in due course.</p>","Truro and Falmouth","Sarah Newton",,"2017-09-07T16:01:41.777Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756902/answer","Biography information for Sarah Newton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756902/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756902/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2017-09-04","Poisons Act 1972","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what plans she has to amend the Poisons Act 1972; and if she will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","8171"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756903","Home Office","false","2017-09-12","<p>The Government is very concerned about crime enabled by motorcycle, moped and scooters. On 12 September, together with the Policing and Fire Service Minister Nick Hurd MP, I will co-chair an event, bringing together motor and insurance industry leaders, law enforcement partners, local government agencies, as well as youth charities and other groups, on addressing this emerging threat and to identify actions to reduce this type of crime.</p>","Truro and Falmouth","Sarah Newton","8120","2017-09-12T12:27:24.56Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756903/answer","Biography information for Sarah Newton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756903/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/756903/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2017-09-04","Motorcycles: Crime","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what steps she is taking to tackle criminal use of motorcycles, mopeds and scooters.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","8121"
