"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754585","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-09-06","<p>RAF Northolt maintains extensive links with local community groups where local concerns can be raised. The station invites local community leaders to six monthly meetings of the Community Liaison Group so it can update them on issues such as infrastructure work or expected unusual military aircraft movements.</p><p>Members of the public can contact the station direct by telephone or online and a dedicated officer will investigate their concerns and respond to them.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-09-06T15:57:44.173Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754585/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754585/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754585/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-07-20","RAF Northolt: Aviation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what mechanisms RAF Northolt has in place to manage noise complaints from people under the flight path of places using that airfield.","false","Biography information for Gareth Thomas","Harrow West","Gareth Thomas","6532"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754586","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-09-06","<p>The cost for the whole RAF Northolt project is £35 - £45 million. The cost includes all work on site and is directly comparable to similar commercial projects. The cost of the runway re-surfacing cannot be separated out.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood","6535","2017-09-06T15:57:10.32Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754586/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754586/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754586/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-07-20","RAF Northolt: Aviation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the cost of the runway re-surfacing works at RAF Northolt will be.","false","Biography information for Gareth Thomas","Harrow West","Gareth Thomas","6534"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754587","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-09-06","<p>Until the detailed design is complete this is an unknown quantity. However, all work will be conducted in line with regulatory standards, following Government guidelines and approvals.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-09-06T16:03:50.72Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754587/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754587/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754587/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-07-20","RAF Northolt: Aviation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many tonnes of materials will be excavated from the runway re-surfacing at RAF Northolt; and where that waste will be taken.","false","Biography information for Gareth Thomas","Harrow West","Gareth Thomas","6529"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754588","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-09-06","<p>The amount of lorry movements required to undertake runway re-surfacing works at RAF Northolt is not known. However, all work will be conducted in line with regulatory standards, following government guidelines and approvals.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-09-06T15:58:30.89Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754588/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754588/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/754588/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-07-20","RAF Northolt: Aviation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many lorry movements will be required to undertake the runway re-surfacing works at RAF Northolt.","false","Biography information for Gareth Thomas","Harrow West","Gareth Thomas","6530"
